<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-03-0530 </DOCNO><TEXT>The CR-method for predicting the thermal performance of a building, itsmain limitations and the EA-CR method's improvements are briefly reviewed.A micro-computer program based on these procedures is described. Itsuse as an educational tool is explained and some interesting resultsare reported.</TEXT></DOC>